WEBVTT

00:17.160 --> 00:18.000
Soldiers,

00:18.390 --> 00:19.920
we are the sons of Great Yan!

00:20.350 --> 00:22.750
Born on the grasslands,
we stand above all!

00:23.070 --> 00:25.200
Now, Biantang has broken its promise,

00:25.480 --> 00:27.120
failing to return our Queen

00:27.870 --> 00:30.550
and trampling on our dignity and glory!

00:31.350 --> 00:32.070
Today,

00:32.430 --> 00:36.090
the Black Eagle Army's cavalry
shall raze Biantang to the ground!

00:37.110 --> 00:38.430
Raze Biantang to the ground!

00:38.430 --> 00:39.900
Long live Great Yan!

00:39.920 --> 00:42.790
Raze Biantang to the ground!
Long live Great Yan!

00:42.840 --> 00:45.750
Raze Biantang to the ground!
Long live Great Yan!

00:45.840 --> 00:48.570
Raze Biantang to the ground!
Long live Great Yan!

02:08.530 --> 02:13.500
[REBIRTH]

02:14.050 --> 02:16.530
[Episode 20]

02:22.750 --> 02:23.520
Your Majesty,

02:23.520 --> 02:24.520
an urgent report.

02:26.190 --> 02:26.910
Your Majesty,

02:26.910 --> 02:28.070
Yan Xun, King of Great Yan,

02:28.070 --> 02:30.280
has declared war on us
under the pretext that we're harboring

02:30.280 --> 02:31.470
his queen, Chu Qiao!

02:31.470 --> 02:32.800
He's already broken through
three cities in a row,

02:32.800 --> 02:34.500
and the army is now
bearing down on Longyin Pass.

02:34.500 --> 02:37.190
General Li Qi is fighting desperately,
holding the line!

02:37.190 --> 02:38.590
Yan Xun is brazen enough

02:39.120 --> 02:40.850
to use this as a pretext for war!

02:45.280 --> 02:46.079
Your Majesty,

02:46.190 --> 02:47.630
the situation is critical.

02:47.630 --> 02:49.470
We don't know how much longer Li Qi can
hold the line.

02:49.470 --> 02:51.270
Should we inform General Xiuli?

02:51.430 --> 02:52.680
Qiao is exhausted.

02:53.560 --> 02:54.680
Let her rest well.

02:54.840 --> 02:55.470
We will

02:56.520 --> 02:57.560
deal with Yan Xun.

02:59.240 --> 03:01.840
This subject is willing to go to
Longyin Pass to reinforce General Li.

03:01.840 --> 03:02.430
No.

03:02.800 --> 03:04.310
The court has only just been stabilized.

03:04.310 --> 03:06.400
You're responsible for
the defense of the capital.

03:06.400 --> 03:07.960
Sending you now

03:08.110 --> 03:09.840
would undermine the stability of Tangjing.

03:09.840 --> 03:10.840
But apart from me,

03:11.360 --> 03:13.680
all the other generals
favor peace over war.

03:13.680 --> 03:15.740
I fear that if such generals are sent,

03:16.000 --> 03:17.750
the morale of the soldiers
on the front line will waver,

03:17.750 --> 03:19.680
leaving them unable to resist
Great Yan's Black Eagle Army.

03:19.680 --> 03:20.520
You may leave.

03:21.120 --> 03:22.320
Let me think about it.

03:43.400 --> 03:45.190
Right now, there is only one way

03:46.030 --> 03:47.470
to solve your country's crisis:

03:47.470 --> 03:50.530
reinforce General Li
and fight back against Great Yan.

03:51.360 --> 03:52.640
I know that.

03:53.910 --> 03:55.840
But I've just ascended the throne.

03:56.030 --> 03:57.560
I have very few capable men
at my disposal.

03:57.560 --> 03:58.750
Aside from Sun Di,

03:59.200 --> 04:00.730
the other veteran generals

04:00.960 --> 04:03.800
are all arrogant about their merits
and utterly obstinate.

04:03.800 --> 04:05.080
Then let's make a deal.

04:05.910 --> 04:07.630
I'll help you defeat Great Yan.

04:07.630 --> 04:08.560
In return,

04:09.150 --> 04:10.480
after Yan Xun retreats,

04:10.590 --> 04:11.960
you have to lend me an army.

04:11.960 --> 04:13.490
What do you need an army for?

04:15.240 --> 04:16.100
I have my reasons.

04:16.100 --> 04:18.760
You still have the nerve
to strike a deal with me?

04:21.350 --> 04:23.190
Last time you promised me
the black gold mine.

04:23.190 --> 04:23.720
To this day,

04:23.720 --> 04:25.920
I haven't seen so much as a glimpse
of a gold nugget.

04:25.920 --> 04:27.120
If not for you and Qiao saving me,

04:27.120 --> 04:28.070
do you think I'd even be talking to you?

04:28.070 --> 04:29.070
Once it's done,

04:29.560 --> 04:30.430
I'll return your men

04:30.430 --> 04:32.070
and deliver 30% of the black gold mine

04:32.070 --> 04:33.310
as agreed.

04:36.270 --> 04:38.270
You're not planning to use my troops

04:38.360 --> 04:40.420
to seize the black gold mine, are you?

04:41.070 --> 04:42.330
None of your business.

04:46.510 --> 04:49.430
Aren't you King Ximeng's double?

04:50.720 --> 04:51.720
Could it be...

04:53.680 --> 04:55.740
Could it be that in Ximeng, you're...

04:58.210 --> 04:58.940
I know!

04:59.360 --> 05:01.240
You are nothing more than...

05:02.720 --> 05:04.070
a puppet of King Ximeng.

05:05.830 --> 05:07.920
I didn't expect your position in Ximeng

05:07.920 --> 05:09.360
to be so dire.

05:14.390 --> 05:15.990
Your Majesty guessed right.

05:16.080 --> 05:18.000
Much like your own situation not long ago.

05:18.000 --> 05:18.630
Zhuge Yue,

05:18.630 --> 05:19.890
-You...
-Enough talk.

05:20.060 --> 05:20.860
Do you

05:21.710 --> 05:23.590
accept this deal or not?

05:35.750 --> 05:36.310
I accept.

05:41.360 --> 05:42.600
Where are you going, General Chu?

05:42.600 --> 05:43.800
To the military camp.

05:44.920 --> 05:45.680
General Chu.

05:45.950 --> 05:47.630
I heard today is not a good day to go out.

05:47.630 --> 05:48.680
Why don't you go another day?

05:48.680 --> 05:49.680
Not a good day?

05:52.430 --> 05:54.230
The heavens show unusual signs!

05:58.970 --> 06:00.480
Isn't the sun shining

06:00.800 --> 06:01.860
and everything peaceful?

06:01.860 --> 06:02.710
-General Chu,
-General Chu,

06:02.710 --> 06:04.000
-this is merely a false calm.
-this is merely a false calm.

06:04.000 --> 06:05.170
-In an instant...
-In an instant...

06:05.170 --> 06:05.790
The sky will darken.

06:05.790 --> 06:06.480
Winds will rise!

06:06.480 --> 06:09.280
-A great storm will come!
-A great storm will come!

06:09.600 --> 06:10.330
General Chu!

06:14.240 --> 06:16.800
Song Cheng, the Imperial Guard,
pays respects to you.

06:16.800 --> 06:18.740
I've come to present to you
the gifts bestowed by His Majesty.

06:18.740 --> 06:21.190
These are the gifts
His Majesty has prepared for you.

06:21.190 --> 06:22.240
Thank you, Lord Song.

06:22.240 --> 06:24.240
But I need to go to the military camp.

06:24.830 --> 06:25.600
General Chu,

06:25.920 --> 06:28.240
in addition to these gifts,
His Majesty has decreed

06:28.240 --> 06:29.440
that starting today,

06:29.630 --> 06:31.270
this mansion shall be officially renamed

06:31.270 --> 06:32.680
the "General Xiuli's Mansion."

06:31.880 --> 06:34.180
[General Xiuli's Mansion]

06:35.430 --> 06:36.159
Lord Song,

06:36.560 --> 06:37.750
please thank His Majesty for me.

06:37.750 --> 06:39.270
But I really have urgent matters

06:39.270 --> 06:40.750
and need to go to
the military camp in person.

06:40.750 --> 06:42.880
So I won't go to the palace to thank him.

06:44.240 --> 06:45.240
General Chu!

06:45.830 --> 06:46.560
Today...

06:47.210 --> 06:48.610
is not a good day to go out.

06:50.430 --> 06:52.230
The heavens show unusual signs.

06:52.240 --> 06:53.630
The sky will darken,

06:54.040 --> 06:55.480
winds will rise...

06:59.159 --> 07:00.830
And a great storm is coming.

07:01.240 --> 07:02.000
General Chu!

07:07.870 --> 07:09.830
Your Highness,
congratulations on becoming General Xiuli.

07:09.830 --> 07:11.830
Why don't we celebrate with a drink?

07:12.070 --> 07:12.720
Yes.

07:13.070 --> 07:14.360
Such a happy event—

07:14.360 --> 07:16.160
we should celebrate it properly.

07:16.160 --> 07:17.560
Are you two alright?

07:18.040 --> 07:20.240
-The heavens show unusual signs.
-The heavens show unusual signs.

07:20.240 --> 07:21.270
The sky will darken.

07:21.270 --> 07:22.800
Winds will rise.

07:23.070 --> 07:24.390
And a great storm is coming.

07:24.390 --> 07:26.190
-Not a good day to go out!
-Not a good day to go out!

07:26.190 --> 07:27.450
Not a good day to go out.

07:30.800 --> 07:33.830
You've been doing everything you can
to stop me from going out.

07:33.830 --> 07:35.830
What exactly are you hiding from me?

07:50.560 --> 07:51.190
Xing,

07:51.920 --> 07:52.680
come with me.

08:20.460 --> 08:26.500
[Tangjing]

08:30.360 --> 08:32.419
How can there be so many war refugees?

08:33.360 --> 08:34.000
Open up.

08:34.390 --> 08:35.000
What is it?

08:35.960 --> 08:36.549
Behave!

08:41.840 --> 08:44.770
Yan Xun's army has already
advanced to Longyin Pass.

08:44.790 --> 08:46.720
Biantang's Yuncheng,
Xicheng, and Qiangcheng

08:46.720 --> 08:48.120
have also been breached.

08:48.240 --> 08:50.440
Right now, the officials are all saying

08:51.120 --> 08:53.080
that this war started because of you

08:53.080 --> 08:55.340
and have petitioned Li Ce to hand you over

08:55.360 --> 08:57.020
to appease Great Yan's anger.

08:59.720 --> 09:01.200
Li Ce wants to protect me.

09:03.000 --> 09:04.360
But he shouldn't be stopping me.

09:04.360 --> 09:06.420
I've already discussed it with Li Ce.

09:06.510 --> 09:08.040
I'll fight this war for him.

09:11.870 --> 09:12.550
Beat him!

09:20.630 --> 09:21.270
Stop!

09:21.910 --> 09:22.840
Stop it, all of you!

09:22.840 --> 09:23.390
Stop!

09:25.440 --> 09:26.770
Why are you hitting him?

09:27.080 --> 09:29.080
Who are you? Mind your own business!

09:29.600 --> 09:31.200
I am General Xiuli, Chu Qiao!

09:31.930 --> 09:33.150
Greetings, General Xiuli!

09:33.150 --> 09:34.440
We didn't recognize you earlier,
General Chu.

09:34.440 --> 09:35.550
Please forgive us.

09:35.960 --> 09:37.320
This man stole the vendor's steamed buns,

09:37.320 --> 09:39.030
which is why we were disciplining him.

09:39.030 --> 09:40.760
General, please judge fairly.

09:47.200 --> 09:48.060
What happened?

09:48.710 --> 09:49.590
General Xiuli,

09:49.630 --> 09:52.030
it was him!
He stole my steamed buns first!

10:03.440 --> 10:05.390
I'll buy all your buns.

10:05.910 --> 10:08.040
Distribute them to the refugees here.

10:08.720 --> 10:09.510
Okay, okay.

10:09.720 --> 10:10.910
Thank you, General!

10:16.910 --> 10:17.480
Here.

10:20.130 --> 10:21.530
Here. You must be hungry.

10:29.390 --> 10:30.950
Why did he do that?

10:31.750 --> 10:32.790
You are Chu Qiao?

10:33.270 --> 10:34.530
It's all because of you

10:34.720 --> 10:36.390
that Great Yan is attacking Biantang!

10:36.390 --> 10:37.990
Because of you, we commoners

10:38.100 --> 10:41.100
have lost our homes
and been forced to wander!

10:41.870 --> 10:43.020
She is Chu Qiao!

10:43.050 --> 10:44.320
It's this woman!

10:44.750 --> 10:46.550
She's the one who ruined our lives!

10:46.550 --> 10:48.120
Kill this wicked woman!

10:50.240 --> 10:51.200
Don't hurt them!

10:51.200 --> 10:52.860
They have done nothing wrong!

10:53.870 --> 10:55.440
Why is it so unacceptable

10:55.670 --> 10:57.550
to send reinforcements to General Li?

10:57.550 --> 10:58.350
Your Majesty,

10:58.670 --> 11:00.390
the Black Eagle Army is unstoppable.

11:00.390 --> 11:02.200
Our forces were completely unprepared

11:02.200 --> 11:03.600
and unable to fight back.

11:03.910 --> 11:05.870
If we rashly send reinforcements now,

11:05.870 --> 11:08.030
we will only be sending more soldiers
to their deaths.

11:08.030 --> 11:11.270
Moreover, the King of Great Yan's
true intention is not to conquer us.

11:11.270 --> 11:13.030
If we send troops now,

11:13.510 --> 11:14.550
there will be no room left

11:14.550 --> 11:16.510
f-for negotiation between us.

11:16.510 --> 11:17.870
In this time of national crisis,

11:17.870 --> 11:19.960
Your Majesty must not let
matters of the heart cloud your judgment.

11:19.960 --> 11:21.550
General Xiuli is righteous at heart—

11:21.550 --> 11:23.270
surely she wouldn't wish
for our country to suffer.

11:23.270 --> 11:25.030
The citizens of the realm come first.

11:25.030 --> 11:26.390
Handing over General Chu

11:26.390 --> 11:28.480
in exchange for peace
for the countless citizens—

11:28.480 --> 11:30.150
General Chu will surely understand

11:30.150 --> 11:32.720
Your Majesty's
well-intentioned consideration!

11:32.720 --> 11:34.670
General Chu played a crucial role
in helping me ascend the throne.

11:34.670 --> 11:35.910
If I abandon such a loyal official

11:35.910 --> 11:37.630
in our hour of crisis,

11:37.960 --> 11:40.220
do you want the whole world to ridicule me

11:40.440 --> 11:41.750
for being heartless and ungrateful?

11:41.750 --> 11:42.550
Your Majesty,

11:43.030 --> 11:44.240
this subject has failed you.

11:44.240 --> 11:46.970
I'm willing to
give everything for Your Majesty—

11:47.080 --> 11:48.210
to die on the battlefield

11:48.210 --> 11:50.550
and sacrifice my life without hesitation!

11:50.550 --> 11:54.360
But I cannot gamble with
the lives of tens of thousands

11:54.360 --> 11:55.480
of our soldiers!

11:57.720 --> 11:59.200
I second that!

11:59.550 --> 12:01.150
I second that!

12:01.180 --> 12:03.180
I second that!

12:03.240 --> 12:05.080
I second that!

12:24.440 --> 12:27.600
Officials, you've been discussing
sending me off to Great Yan,

12:27.600 --> 12:28.670
yet none of you thought to inform me,

12:28.670 --> 12:30.270
the very person in question?

12:34.030 --> 12:34.830
Your Majesty,

12:35.080 --> 12:36.240
I have a gift

12:36.440 --> 12:38.300
to present to the officials here.

12:38.510 --> 12:40.170
Please go ahead, General Chu.

12:45.910 --> 12:47.840
I, Chu Qiao,

12:48.510 --> 12:50.390
have abducted all of your wives.

12:51.150 --> 12:51.840
What?

12:51.840 --> 12:52.240
You...

12:52.670 --> 12:54.550
T-This is outrageous!

12:57.390 --> 12:58.190
Your Majesty,

12:58.550 --> 13:00.150
General Xiuli has abducted
the families of court officials.

13:00.150 --> 13:01.350
This is a grave crime!

13:01.840 --> 13:03.080
Please uphold justice, Your Majesty!

13:03.080 --> 13:05.510
How could you resort to
such despicable tactics?

13:05.510 --> 13:07.240
Shameful! Outrageous!

13:07.240 --> 13:07.970
General Chu,

13:10.150 --> 13:12.510
that's my wife's coral hairpin, right?

13:12.630 --> 13:13.840
I'm on your side.

13:13.920 --> 13:15.830
Why did you take my wife too?

13:16.390 --> 13:17.990
Please calm down, everyone.

13:18.120 --> 13:18.720
I only wish

13:19.360 --> 13:21.290
to make a point to His Majesty here.

13:21.920 --> 13:24.910
I have no grudge whatsoever against
the wives of the officials present,

13:24.910 --> 13:26.680
nor any intention of harming them.

13:26.680 --> 13:27.920
I simply ask that you

13:28.270 --> 13:31.750
cease submitting petitions to
send me to Great Yan as a hostage.

13:31.750 --> 13:33.350
Despicable and ridiculous!

13:33.600 --> 13:34.400
Your Majesty,

13:34.720 --> 13:37.150
this matter concerns
the fate of our country.

13:37.150 --> 13:39.270
For generations,
my family has been loyal to the country

13:39.270 --> 13:40.600
through life and death!

13:40.630 --> 13:43.270
I will never change my counsel
to the throne

13:44.120 --> 13:45.840
because of my wife's safety.

13:46.270 --> 13:47.070
I second that.

13:47.150 --> 13:48.600
The safety of one family
is a small matter—

13:48.600 --> 13:50.240
the fate of Biantang is paramount!

13:50.240 --> 13:52.150
How noble and righteous

13:52.150 --> 13:53.080
you all are!

13:53.200 --> 13:54.460
To die for His Majesty,

13:55.080 --> 13:56.670
I will not hesitate!

13:56.670 --> 13:57.630
Well said!

13:58.550 --> 13:59.440
Officials,

14:00.150 --> 14:02.350
if none of you would
change your political stance

14:02.350 --> 14:04.010
for the sake of your own wives,

14:04.040 --> 14:05.310
then why do you believe

14:05.840 --> 14:07.360
that the King of Great Yan

14:07.630 --> 14:10.320
would stop the war for a woman like me?

14:12.510 --> 14:15.170
What General Chu says
is precisely what I think.

14:15.630 --> 14:17.750
Yan Xun is the King of Great Yan.

14:19.120 --> 14:21.650
Back then, he fled back
to Great Yan all alone,

14:22.030 --> 14:23.430
led the Black Eagle Army,

14:23.440 --> 14:25.000
and conquered
half of Great Yong's territory.

14:25.000 --> 14:26.130
That is proof enough

14:26.390 --> 14:27.030
that he is a man

14:27.030 --> 14:28.830
of both intellect and ambition.

14:29.600 --> 14:32.150
Yuncheng, Xicheng, and Qiangcheng

14:32.430 --> 14:34.630
lie in Biantang's most fertile region.

14:34.910 --> 14:35.960
Great Yan is harsh and barren.

14:35.960 --> 14:37.320
By seizing these three cities,

14:37.320 --> 14:39.520
they will establish their new granary.

14:39.720 --> 14:41.390
Longyin Pass connects these three cities

14:41.390 --> 14:42.910
and forms a defensive line.

14:42.910 --> 14:44.390
It's both Biantang's strategic lifeline

14:44.390 --> 14:46.240
and the shield protecting Great Yong.

14:46.240 --> 14:47.600
If Longyin Pass falls,

14:47.790 --> 14:50.450
the north of Biantang
will fall without a fight.

14:50.750 --> 14:51.880
When the time comes,

14:52.390 --> 14:54.390
if Yan Xun launches
a pincer attack on Great Yong,

14:54.390 --> 14:56.120
it will be child's play for him.

14:58.840 --> 15:00.570
Yan Xun is fiercely ambitious!

15:01.310 --> 15:02.160
Our Biantang

15:02.960 --> 15:04.000
must not yield!

15:05.910 --> 15:07.580
Please, Your Majesty, give the order

15:07.580 --> 15:09.530
to appoint me as commander-in-chief

15:09.530 --> 15:10.790
to shoulder this burden on your behalf

15:10.790 --> 15:12.510
and lead the campaign to Longyin Pass!

15:12.510 --> 15:13.710
If I have not repelled

15:13.790 --> 15:15.450
the Yan Army within one month,

15:15.680 --> 15:17.410
I will leave Biantang on my own!

15:33.720 --> 15:35.520
This campaign will be grueling.

15:35.550 --> 15:37.810
I had not intended to trouble you with it.

15:38.000 --> 15:39.840
Since Your Majesty has decided to fight,

15:39.840 --> 15:41.440
I am willing to lead the army!

15:48.670 --> 15:51.440
The General Xiuli's Mansion
is truly grand.

15:51.960 --> 15:53.030
The garden alone

15:53.390 --> 15:54.960
is bigger than my house.

15:55.480 --> 15:57.720
Duchess, Marchioness,

15:58.080 --> 15:59.320
don't you think so?

15:59.630 --> 16:01.630
It's indeed grand!

16:01.630 --> 16:03.270
Extremely grand.

16:03.630 --> 16:04.440
Right?

16:04.710 --> 16:09.170
[Xu Su's Wife]

16:05.360 --> 16:07.840
General Chu hasn't been here very long,

16:07.840 --> 16:09.170
yet she's put my home...

16:10.600 --> 16:13.550
put all of our homes to shame.

16:13.810 --> 16:15.650
[Sun Di's Wife]

16:15.320 --> 16:16.230
Mrs. Sun,

16:16.550 --> 16:19.790
I don't think
your residence is this large, right?

16:22.200 --> 16:23.120
Mrs. Xu,

16:23.320 --> 16:24.450
that's quite a joke.

16:25.030 --> 16:28.320
This residence used to be
the Crown Prince's mansion.

16:28.960 --> 16:31.720
Its grandeur belongs to His Majesty.

16:32.150 --> 16:34.510
How could our residences possibly compare?

16:34.510 --> 16:37.560
Could it be that you want to
outshine His Majesty?

16:37.650 --> 16:39.500
What are you talking about, Mrs. Sun?

16:39.500 --> 16:41.500
How dare I compare with His Majesty?

16:52.030 --> 16:55.200
Today's grapes are so sour!

16:55.720 --> 16:57.080
They're a hundred times

16:57.200 --> 16:59.800
more sour than vinegar!

17:00.440 --> 17:01.550
Try one.

17:04.680 --> 17:05.720
It's quite sour.

17:06.160 --> 17:06.960
Mrs. Xu,

17:07.440 --> 17:08.440
have one too.

17:21.550 --> 17:22.589
-What...
-Well...

17:22.589 --> 17:23.400
Ladies,

17:23.589 --> 17:24.550
it's about time.

17:24.750 --> 17:25.680
General Xiuli

17:25.710 --> 17:27.829
has prepared gifts for you in advance.

17:27.829 --> 17:29.360
Thank you for coming today.

17:29.440 --> 17:30.700
The borrowed hairpins

17:30.790 --> 17:33.050
will be sent to your residences tonight.

17:34.240 --> 17:34.880
Honey!

17:35.920 --> 17:36.640
Honey!

17:39.200 --> 17:41.070
Where have you been all afternoon?

17:41.070 --> 17:42.310
I couldn't find you anywhere.

17:42.310 --> 17:44.310
I just went to General Xiuli's mansion

17:44.310 --> 17:45.350
for some tea.

17:45.680 --> 17:47.510
The general even gave me a gift.

17:47.510 --> 17:49.110
All your favorite pastries.

17:51.000 --> 17:51.640
Tea?

17:52.640 --> 17:53.660
When you were there,

17:53.660 --> 17:55.060
did you sense any danger?

17:55.160 --> 17:57.680
Or any hidden schemes or lurking threats?

17:57.680 --> 17:58.960
What has gotten into you?

17:58.960 --> 18:00.550
I just went to have some tea.

18:00.740 --> 18:02.700
What could possibly have happened?

18:02.700 --> 18:03.950
I was worried.

18:04.720 --> 18:06.650
The situation has been unstable lately.

18:06.650 --> 18:08.450
I was concerned for your safety.

18:09.680 --> 18:11.660
What is there to be so anxious about?

18:11.660 --> 18:13.310
I came back perfectly fine, didn't I?

18:13.310 --> 18:14.570
Come on, let's go home.

18:14.570 --> 18:15.630
I was worried sick.

18:29.640 --> 18:30.270
Xing.

18:35.480 --> 18:36.210
What's this?

18:38.440 --> 18:40.370
They're the Sun-Moon Twin Swords.

18:40.750 --> 18:42.080
The sun represents you,

18:42.240 --> 18:43.770
and the moon represents me.

18:48.590 --> 18:49.990
Sun-Moon Twin Swords...

18:50.790 --> 18:52.920
Is there anything special about them?

18:53.480 --> 18:55.790
Our swords—the Fading Crimson Sword
and the Moon-breaking Sword—

18:55.790 --> 18:57.450
one fell into the frozen lake,

18:57.680 --> 18:59.960
and the other was sent back
to Qingshan Manor.

18:59.960 --> 19:01.400
I had them retrieved

19:01.400 --> 19:02.800
through great hardship,

19:02.830 --> 19:04.360
then melted down and forged

19:04.690 --> 19:06.010
into these two swords.

19:09.200 --> 19:09.960
What else?

19:13.590 --> 19:14.550
They represent

19:16.030 --> 19:17.830
that we will always be together.

19:20.960 --> 19:21.790
You're not

19:22.440 --> 19:24.400
just my Xing anymore.

19:24.720 --> 19:27.070
You are General Xiuli—capable of
illuminating the path for many people.

19:27.070 --> 19:29.110
These two swords and I

19:29.960 --> 19:32.820
will accompany you
on the campaign to Longyin Pass,

19:32.880 --> 19:34.140
fighting at your side.

20:14.160 --> 20:14.920
Mr. Xiao,

20:15.830 --> 20:17.760
please give me some Huiyuan Pills.

20:19.420 --> 20:21.620
Taking too many of those will kill you.

20:23.200 --> 20:25.550
I must stay alive to
fight this battle through alongside Xing.

20:25.550 --> 20:27.160
You must give them to me no matter what.

20:27.160 --> 20:28.560
If General Chu finds out,

20:28.880 --> 20:30.210
we'll both be finished.

20:30.690 --> 20:31.620
If I die,

20:32.140 --> 20:34.200
you may use my body for your research.

20:35.070 --> 20:36.390
Really? You promise?

20:39.550 --> 20:41.190
W-What kind of person do you take me for?

20:41.190 --> 20:42.970
I would absolutely never agree
to something like this.

20:42.970 --> 20:43.580
I...

20:49.070 --> 20:49.680
You...

20:50.790 --> 20:52.250
are not lying to me, right?

20:54.350 --> 20:55.000
No.

20:57.850 --> 20:58.850
No, no, no.

20:59.880 --> 21:01.640
I would absolutely never agree
to something like this.

21:01.640 --> 21:03.200
I-I am a person of principles!

21:03.200 --> 21:03.590
Besides...

21:03.590 --> 21:04.480
What if I give you

21:04.480 --> 21:05.940
a reason you can't refuse?

21:07.680 --> 21:08.480
This battle

21:08.790 --> 21:10.720
concerns the lives of millions.

21:10.830 --> 21:11.880
If we lose,

21:12.510 --> 21:14.240
Biantang will be laid to ruin,

21:14.550 --> 21:16.550
with bodies strewn across the land.

21:17.720 --> 21:19.780
There are four Huiyuan Pills inside.

21:25.710 --> 21:26.910
Take them sparingly.

21:26.960 --> 21:28.090
If you take them all,

21:28.640 --> 21:29.700
you'll really die.

21:33.680 --> 21:34.740
You must remember,

21:34.840 --> 21:36.170
if anything happens...

21:41.110 --> 21:41.720
Go.

21:44.270 --> 21:45.400
Thank you, Mr. Xiao.

21:47.510 --> 21:50.060
I've painstakingly hand-picked

21:50.080 --> 21:52.140
these 20,000 elite soldiers myself.

21:52.830 --> 21:54.920
You'd better count them carefully.

21:55.120 --> 21:56.050
Elite soldiers?

21:56.200 --> 21:57.640
From what I see, most of them

21:57.640 --> 21:58.920
are disabled veterans

21:59.200 --> 22:00.960
and untrained recruits.

22:01.200 --> 22:02.070
General Chu,

22:03.070 --> 22:04.720
Biantang may be prosperous,

22:04.830 --> 22:06.140
but we haven't fought

22:06.270 --> 22:08.310
a large-scale war in a long time.

22:08.590 --> 22:09.880
This conflict arose suddenly,

22:09.880 --> 22:11.830
so the troops we are able to
mobilize are limited.

22:11.830 --> 22:14.400
You're the renowned General Xiuli,

22:14.750 --> 22:16.750
who has won countless battles.

22:17.040 --> 22:19.030
As long as you personally lead the army,

22:19.030 --> 22:20.270
surely the Great Yan Army

22:20.270 --> 22:22.200
will retreat without a fight.

22:22.480 --> 22:23.200
Xu Su,

22:24.000 --> 22:26.070
you're clearly trying to
sabotage the Xiuli Army!

22:26.070 --> 22:27.270
Deputy Commander He,

22:27.350 --> 22:29.070
I outrank you by two levels,

22:29.070 --> 22:31.070
yet you dare address me by my name?

22:31.130 --> 22:32.650
That's insubordination!

22:33.030 --> 22:34.960
You'd better remember your place!

22:35.070 --> 22:36.830
You are Biantang's Xiuli Army,

22:36.960 --> 22:38.640
not someone's private army!

22:40.200 --> 22:42.590
His Majesty has arrived!

22:49.510 --> 22:50.240
You may rise.

22:54.600 --> 22:55.230
Qiao,

22:55.980 --> 22:58.580
I'm giving
these 3,000 imperial guards to you.

22:59.030 --> 23:00.290
These 3,000 guards are

23:00.710 --> 23:02.910
the most elite force in all of Biantang.

23:03.270 --> 23:05.200
They shall guard you and the people

23:06.070 --> 23:08.790
of Longyin Pass as they would guard me.

23:09.510 --> 23:10.150
Qiao,

23:10.680 --> 23:11.880
you and the Xiuli Army

23:12.750 --> 23:14.240
are the hope of Biantang.

23:16.270 --> 23:17.670
Thank you, Your Majesty.

23:17.920 --> 23:19.120
Get up quickly, Qiao.

23:26.750 --> 23:28.000
March out!

23:46.420 --> 23:48.750
[Tangjing]

24:07.850 --> 24:08.720
General Chu,
you must've had a long journey.

24:08.720 --> 24:09.510
-General Chu.
-General Chu.

24:09.510 --> 24:11.110
General Li, you've worked hard.

24:11.110 --> 24:11.840
General Chu,

24:11.920 --> 24:13.030
we've been locked in this standoff

24:13.030 --> 24:14.760
with Great Yan for over a month.

24:14.880 --> 24:16.830
Longyin Pass is easy to defend
and hard to attack,

24:16.830 --> 24:18.200
but if this stalemate continues,

24:18.200 --> 24:20.660
the garrison alone
won't be able to hold out.

24:21.110 --> 24:21.790
General Li,

24:22.240 --> 24:24.160
I'll arrange for the Xiuli Army
to relieve your troops first,

24:24.160 --> 24:25.440
so you can rest

24:25.460 --> 24:26.990
and recover your strength.

24:27.350 --> 24:29.550
We'll follow your orders, General Chu!

24:52.550 --> 24:54.270
This wound has already begun to fester.

24:54.270 --> 24:56.070
It must be treated immediately.

24:56.310 --> 24:58.310
This medicinal liquor is very strong.

24:58.310 --> 24:59.510
You'll need to endure some pain.

24:59.510 --> 25:02.240
I've survived the blades
of Great Yan's savages.

25:02.640 --> 25:03.440
What's

25:04.000 --> 25:05.330
a little pain like this?

25:14.640 --> 25:16.940
I'll come to remove
the bandages in three days.

25:16.940 --> 25:19.340
I must remove the pus
and dead tissue first.

25:24.950 --> 25:26.150
Thank you, thank you!

25:39.020 --> 25:40.110
It's getting cold.

25:40.160 --> 25:42.560
In this environment, I'm afraid the wounds

25:42.920 --> 25:44.180
may not heal properly.

25:45.030 --> 25:45.680
Hurry.

25:49.870 --> 25:51.640
Add more charcoal every six hours

25:51.640 --> 25:52.610
to maintain the temperature here.

25:52.610 --> 25:53.810
-Yes, sir.
-Yes, sir.

26:07.840 --> 26:08.440
Look,

26:08.920 --> 26:10.550
Longyin Pass is the gateway to Biantang.

26:10.550 --> 26:11.750
If Great Yan wants to conquer Biantang,

26:11.750 --> 26:13.960
this place should've been
their first target.

26:13.960 --> 26:15.640
But earlier, the Yan Army captured
three cities in succession,

26:15.640 --> 26:16.830
taking a longer route

26:16.830 --> 26:18.440
through the northeast of Biantang.

26:18.440 --> 26:20.930
That's precisely because Longyin Pass is
shielded by mountains—

26:20.930 --> 26:21.830
easy to defend and hard to attack.

26:21.830 --> 26:22.480
So,

26:23.590 --> 26:25.270
as long as we hold Longyin Pass,

26:25.270 --> 26:26.640
the Great Yan army
won't be able to hold out

26:26.640 --> 26:27.830
and will retreat on its own.

26:27.830 --> 26:28.480
Exactly.

26:29.200 --> 26:30.600
General Chu, Lord Zhuge,

26:30.920 --> 26:31.940
the battle for Longyin Pass

26:31.940 --> 26:33.680
won't be over anytime soon.

26:33.750 --> 26:35.750
The military reports can wait.

26:36.200 --> 26:37.200
Let's eat first.

26:37.270 --> 26:38.000
Early this morning, he

26:38.000 --> 26:39.510
went to the woods to hunt some game,

26:39.510 --> 26:41.510
especially to nourish your health.

26:49.480 --> 26:50.660
What are you saying?

26:50.790 --> 26:52.120
Say that again!

26:52.510 --> 26:53.400
Say that again!

26:53.400 --> 26:54.030
Stop it!

26:54.930 --> 26:56.160
Come on! Still acting tough, huh?

26:56.160 --> 26:57.310
Say that again if you dare!

26:57.310 --> 26:58.270
What's going on here?

26:58.270 --> 26:59.160
General Chu,

26:59.460 --> 27:01.050
they said we're useless freeloaders!

27:01.050 --> 27:02.310
You've been here for so many days,

27:02.310 --> 27:03.360
yet you never go out to fight!

27:03.360 --> 27:05.440
You said His Majesty
sent you to support us,

27:05.440 --> 27:06.310
but what did you bring?

27:06.310 --> 27:07.790
Just your mouths!

27:08.050 --> 27:08.560
Exactly!

27:08.560 --> 27:10.160
You're eating our military rations!

27:10.160 --> 27:11.270
If this drags on,

27:11.270 --> 27:12.480
we won't even have enough food!

27:12.480 --> 27:13.720
How are we supposed to defeat Great Yan?

27:13.720 --> 27:14.830
How are we supposed to protect Biantang?

27:14.830 --> 27:16.200
How are we supposed to
protect His Majesty?

27:16.200 --> 27:18.270
You are just useless freeloaders!

27:18.270 --> 27:19.400
Say that again!

27:19.960 --> 27:20.920
Say that again!

27:21.440 --> 27:22.110
Stop!

27:23.400 --> 27:24.750
You're totally useless!

27:24.750 --> 27:25.550
He Xiao!

27:26.720 --> 27:28.920
Has our grain supply still not arrived?

27:30.160 --> 27:30.960
General Chu,

27:31.680 --> 27:33.720
the supply convoy has somehow
been delayed for 10 days,

27:33.720 --> 27:35.180
and there is still no news.

27:35.400 --> 27:36.790
The grain we brought with the army

27:36.790 --> 27:37.920
has long been used up.

27:37.920 --> 27:40.320
We're indeed using General Li's supplies.

27:40.440 --> 27:41.960
General Li was afraid you'd worry,

27:41.960 --> 27:43.490
so he didn't let us tell you.

28:13.390 --> 28:14.020
Minglu,

28:14.550 --> 28:16.970
have someone send
this dispatch out tonight.

28:16.970 --> 28:18.200
Make it extremely urgent.

28:18.200 --> 28:19.720
We'll send out a dispatch every day

28:19.720 --> 28:21.250
until the supplies arrive.

28:22.130 --> 28:22.760
Yes.

28:25.160 --> 28:25.840
Shiyi.

28:28.550 --> 28:29.640
Yes, Young Master?

28:30.160 --> 28:30.920
Tell me,

28:31.270 --> 28:33.590
how was this year's harvest in Great Yong?

28:33.590 --> 28:35.440
Why are you asking that, Young Master?

28:35.440 --> 28:36.270
Take this

28:36.270 --> 28:38.000
and go to the Qilin Bank
in Yancheng of Great Yong.

28:38.000 --> 28:40.110
I have some land deeds and deposit slips
kept there.

28:40.110 --> 28:41.410
By any means necessary,

28:41.410 --> 28:44.160
procure provisions from Biantang
and Great Yong, regardless of cost.

28:44.160 --> 28:45.350
As quickly as you can.

28:45.350 --> 28:46.410
Yes, Young Master.

28:49.270 --> 28:50.930
How much grain is in this cart?

28:51.190 --> 28:52.680
Northern Biantang has experienced
heavy rains this year.

28:52.680 --> 28:53.950
In the Red River Valley area,

28:53.950 --> 28:55.110
we encountered over 10 days of heavy rain,

28:55.110 --> 28:56.190
which caused the delay.

28:56.190 --> 28:57.400
But rest assured, General Chu.

28:57.400 --> 28:58.660
His Majesty and Lord Xu

28:58.680 --> 29:00.200
have personally instructed us.

29:00.200 --> 29:02.400
There will be absolutely no problems
with the rations.

29:02.400 --> 29:04.400
Have they all been counted clearly?

29:05.080 --> 29:06.280
Yes, no problem.

29:07.400 --> 29:09.330
They've already been registered.

29:09.960 --> 29:12.020
General Chu, this grain is not right!

29:17.310 --> 29:18.040
General Chu.

29:19.440 --> 29:21.270
What on earth is the meaning of this?

29:21.270 --> 29:22.870
General Chu, why ask
when you already know the answer?

29:22.870 --> 29:24.000
Biantang has had a lot of rain this year.

29:24.000 --> 29:25.190
The harvest was already poor.

29:25.190 --> 29:26.740
General Li Qi has been fighting

29:26.740 --> 29:27.880
the Yan Army for months.

29:27.880 --> 29:29.590
Now His Majesty has suddenly
ordered reinforcements.

29:29.590 --> 29:30.830
That's 20,000 more mouths to feed.

29:30.830 --> 29:32.590
Where can we get so much grain
on such short notice?

29:32.590 --> 29:33.510
This is clearly Xu Su

29:33.510 --> 29:36.840
deliberately making things difficult
for our General Chu!

29:37.080 --> 29:39.740
Everyone, open the sacks
and inspect the grain!

29:44.110 --> 29:45.370
It's all adulterated.

29:47.920 --> 29:48.640
Stop them!

29:49.030 --> 29:49.750
Stop!

29:49.920 --> 29:51.620
Seizing military grain
is a capital offense!

29:51.620 --> 29:52.690
Don't hurt them!

30:00.550 --> 30:01.750
These are refugees who fled

30:01.750 --> 30:03.410
from the three fallen cities.

30:03.680 --> 30:05.540
The Yan Army occupied the cities.

30:05.880 --> 30:07.680
They have no food and no shelter.

30:07.710 --> 30:10.160
They could only flee south,
beyond Longyin Pass.

30:10.160 --> 30:11.400
Normally, during wartime,

30:11.400 --> 30:12.480
refugees shouldn't
be allowed into the city—

30:12.480 --> 30:14.810
that's the best policy to secure the rear.

30:14.830 --> 30:16.490
General Li Qi couldn't bear it

30:16.680 --> 30:18.940
and ordered that they not be driven away.

30:19.640 --> 30:22.830
Take out my grain rations
and distribute them among the refugees.

30:22.830 --> 30:23.830
From tomorrow on,

30:24.110 --> 30:25.750
I'll eat with the soldiers.

30:26.270 --> 30:28.800
No more separate cooking
in the command tent.

30:30.880 --> 30:32.340
Our intelligence reports

30:32.400 --> 30:34.720
that Chu Qiao's troops
have been here for over 10 days,

30:34.720 --> 30:36.050
yet she has made no move.

30:36.520 --> 30:37.920
She must be planning to outlast us
in this stalemate.

30:37.920 --> 30:39.720
I know how Chu conducts warfare.

30:40.370 --> 30:43.750
Given the current situation,
Biantang lies behind Longyin Pass.

30:43.750 --> 30:45.050
As long as they hold the pass,

30:45.050 --> 30:46.480
there's no need to deploy troops.

30:46.480 --> 30:49.640
But the longer this drags on,
the more it works against us.

30:49.640 --> 30:52.000
Spread word among the refugees
and civilians in Longyin Pass—

30:52.000 --> 30:55.070
tell them that
as long as General Chu is willing to

30:55.310 --> 30:56.310
surrender herself to Great Yan,

30:56.310 --> 30:58.070
Great Yan will withdraw its troops

30:58.070 --> 31:00.130
and leave them completely unharmed.

31:02.440 --> 31:03.200
Cheng Yuan,

31:04.980 --> 31:06.950
you don't still think

31:07.830 --> 31:11.110
I mobilized such a large army
to fight this war

31:11.680 --> 31:13.240
just for Chu, do you?

31:13.720 --> 31:16.440
I know Chu Qiao is only a pretext.

31:16.750 --> 31:18.240
Your Majesty's real objective

31:18.240 --> 31:21.880
is to seize the three granary cities
of Yuncheng, Xicheng, and Qiangcheng

31:21.880 --> 31:22.830
from Biantang.

31:23.070 --> 31:24.000
More than that,

31:24.750 --> 31:26.480
once we take Longyin Pass,

31:26.790 --> 31:29.240
Biantang's forces will be driven south
of the Red River.

31:29.240 --> 31:30.790
Then we can launch a pincer attack

31:30.790 --> 31:32.520
and conquer Great Yong as well.

31:33.350 --> 31:34.550
Your Majesty is wise.

31:45.200 --> 31:45.880
Cheng Yuan.

31:49.350 --> 31:50.250
You and Chu

31:51.030 --> 31:53.290
are both the most important people to me.

31:53.750 --> 31:56.010
I hope you two
can get along in the future.

31:57.880 --> 32:00.920
I miss those days
after we left Zhenhuangcheng,

32:01.320 --> 32:03.650
when you two were still my right-hand men.

32:05.240 --> 32:08.680
Back then,
the Black Eagle Army was unstoppable.

32:10.110 --> 32:11.160
We came so close

32:12.430 --> 32:16.360
to breaking through Great Yong's
final line of defense several times.

32:18.310 --> 32:19.110
Your Majesty,

32:19.210 --> 32:19.920
there will surely come a day

32:19.920 --> 32:21.780
when we truly conquer Great Yong.

32:42.720 --> 32:44.000
What do you think you're doing?

32:44.000 --> 32:45.000
You can't gather here!

32:45.000 --> 32:46.650
We want to see General Chu!

32:46.670 --> 32:48.000
We want to see General Chu!

32:48.000 --> 32:49.680
We won't leave until we see General Chu!

32:49.680 --> 32:51.030
We won't leave until we see her!

32:51.030 --> 32:52.640
Let us see General Chu!

32:52.640 --> 32:54.070
Please let us see General Chu!

32:54.070 --> 32:55.530
We want to see General Chu!

33:00.750 --> 33:02.150
It's getting colder now.

33:02.550 --> 33:04.600
Biantang soldiers aren't used to the cold.

33:04.600 --> 33:05.430
If we don't solve

33:05.430 --> 33:07.350
the problem of
provisions and military supplies,

33:07.350 --> 33:08.400
I'm afraid

33:09.030 --> 33:10.640
we may collapse before Great Yan does.

33:10.640 --> 33:12.270
Yue Shiyi just returned yesterday.

33:12.270 --> 33:14.270
He's procured 500 dans of provisions
from southern Great Yong

33:14.270 --> 33:15.680
and eastern Biantang.

33:16.480 --> 33:17.400
No matter what,

33:17.550 --> 33:18.750
we can get through the next few days.

33:18.750 --> 33:19.480
General Chu!

33:20.590 --> 33:21.240
He Xiao.

33:21.680 --> 33:22.400
What's wrong?

33:22.400 --> 33:24.080
Yan Xun has spread word inside the pass

33:24.080 --> 33:25.750
that as long as you
are willing to surrender,

33:25.750 --> 33:27.020
he will withdraw his troops immediately.

33:27.020 --> 33:27.630
Now, outside the camp,

33:27.630 --> 33:30.430
crowds of civilians
are demanding you surrender.

33:39.640 --> 33:40.640
It's General Chu.

33:41.010 --> 33:42.210
General Chu has come!

33:42.600 --> 33:43.800
General Chu has come.

33:44.240 --> 33:44.900
She's here!

33:45.400 --> 33:46.240
General Chu!

33:46.680 --> 33:48.030
General Chu, save us!

33:48.270 --> 33:49.870
General Chu, please save us!

33:50.000 --> 33:50.830
General Chu!

33:51.070 --> 33:51.750
Please save us!

33:51.750 --> 33:52.680
Everyone, please don't kneel!

33:52.680 --> 33:53.640
Get up quickly!

33:53.640 --> 33:54.400
General Chu,

33:54.790 --> 33:55.810
the King of Great Yan said

33:55.810 --> 33:56.920
that as long as you go with him,

33:56.920 --> 33:57.920
he will withdraw.

33:58.980 --> 34:01.460
Please, save us.

34:01.750 --> 34:02.750
General Chu,

34:02.920 --> 34:04.160
I'm from Shenzhou.

34:04.640 --> 34:08.280
My daughter and uncle
are still in Shenzhou.

34:08.550 --> 34:11.400
I don't know if they are dead or alive.

34:11.830 --> 34:13.380
Please,

34:13.920 --> 34:15.070
General Chu!

34:15.480 --> 34:16.800
I kowtow to you!

34:16.800 --> 34:17.510
Granny,

34:17.510 --> 34:18.550
please get up!

34:19.360 --> 34:20.880
General Chu, please

34:20.880 --> 34:22.110
save us!

34:23.440 --> 34:26.030
Please save us, General Chu!

34:31.690 --> 34:33.810
Stop begging her, everyone!

34:34.440 --> 34:35.590
A woman like her

34:35.760 --> 34:37.670
doesn't care if we live or die!

34:38.320 --> 34:39.880
Look at what she is wearing,

34:39.880 --> 34:42.030
and look at what we're wearing!

34:42.510 --> 34:43.739
She's got our Emperor

34:43.770 --> 34:45.860
completely under her spell!

34:45.920 --> 34:47.320
Even the King of Great Yan

34:47.510 --> 34:49.100
is captivated by her!

34:49.190 --> 34:51.070
As long as we offer her
to the King of Great Yan,

34:51.070 --> 34:52.320
we'll all be saved!

34:52.560 --> 34:53.560
Seize her!

34:56.190 --> 34:57.390
All of you, step back!

34:57.440 --> 34:58.150
Step back!

34:58.760 --> 34:59.190
Step back!

34:59.190 --> 35:00.150
What are you doing?

35:00.150 --> 35:00.880
What are you doing?

35:00.880 --> 35:02.000
Don't come forward anymore!

35:02.000 --> 35:02.800
Get back now!

35:19.630 --> 35:20.320
Yan,

35:21.480 --> 35:23.010
I don't have much time left.

35:23.280 --> 35:25.550
Now I tell you the truth

35:26.240 --> 35:28.920
because you have the right
to know your origins.

35:29.840 --> 35:31.630
I was born into the royal family

35:32.470 --> 35:35.590
and was drawn into
far too many struggles for power.

35:37.000 --> 35:38.190
I also know full well

35:38.190 --> 35:40.880
that the truth will only bring you
more pain.

35:41.590 --> 35:42.190
You,

35:43.000 --> 35:43.590
I,

35:44.320 --> 35:46.280
and even your birth mother—

35:46.920 --> 35:48.150
the Empress—

35:49.360 --> 35:51.420
none of us could do anything about it.

35:52.370 --> 35:53.370
All we can do

35:53.390 --> 35:56.510
is take this secret with us
as we grow old—

35:57.150 --> 35:58.360
and into the grave.

36:05.110 --> 36:05.970
Your Highness.

36:06.070 --> 36:06.670
Matron,

36:07.150 --> 36:09.030
is Her Majesty still unwilling to see me?

36:09.030 --> 36:10.890
Her Majesty has agreed to see you.

36:10.890 --> 36:11.890
But...

36:12.230 --> 36:13.110
But what?

36:13.960 --> 36:15.760
Her Majesty is not feeling well.

36:15.820 --> 36:19.420
After Your Highness pays your respects,
you should leave early.

36:20.320 --> 36:21.520
Don't worry, Matron.

36:21.760 --> 36:24.160
I'll leave
as soon as I've paid my respects.

36:40.110 --> 36:42.920
I, Li Yan, pay my respects
to Your Majesty.

36:44.840 --> 36:47.180
By your decree,
I remained in Jincheng

36:47.200 --> 36:49.530
for three years to guard my father's tomb.

36:49.550 --> 36:51.670
Now that I've just returned to Tangjing,

36:51.670 --> 36:53.130
I came specifically to...

36:54.350 --> 36:56.210
to pay my respects to Your Majesty

36:56.590 --> 36:58.250
and to thank you for your care.

36:59.000 --> 37:00.600
You came all the way to see me—

37:01.110 --> 37:03.170
surely not merely to show gratitude.

37:05.550 --> 37:08.480
What did the Prince of Chang say to you
before he died?

37:10.230 --> 37:11.690
Raise your head and speak.

37:21.880 --> 37:23.880
Before my father died, he told me...

37:25.070 --> 37:25.760
He said...

37:27.280 --> 37:28.550
He said I'm actually

37:28.550 --> 37:29.550
Your Majesty's...

37:29.550 --> 37:30.190
Li Yan!

37:42.880 --> 37:45.510
What your father said is not important.

37:46.400 --> 37:49.590
Your father was
the late Prince of Chang of Jincheng.

37:50.080 --> 37:52.480
His Majesty,
honoring the brotherhood between them

37:52.480 --> 37:54.540
and considering you are his only son,

37:54.880 --> 37:57.110
made an exception and appointed you
a commandery prince.

37:57.110 --> 37:58.030
Who you are—

37:59.230 --> 38:00.760
don't you know it yourself?

38:02.030 --> 38:02.830
Your Majesty,

38:03.360 --> 38:05.220
I don't understand what you mean.

38:05.430 --> 38:07.760
I know why you've been seeking an audience

38:08.190 --> 38:09.510
with me day after day

38:09.510 --> 38:11.400
since your return from Jincheng.

38:12.670 --> 38:13.480
Your Majesty, I...

38:13.480 --> 38:14.670
I agreed to see you

38:14.840 --> 38:16.900
because I want to tell you something.

38:17.590 --> 38:18.990
In this imperial palace,

38:20.070 --> 38:20.760
power,

38:21.230 --> 38:22.000
titles,

38:22.350 --> 38:23.750
and His Majesty's favor—

38:24.510 --> 38:25.840
every single one of them

38:26.030 --> 38:27.880
is more important than blood ties.

38:27.880 --> 38:29.540
When the Prince of Chang died,

38:29.880 --> 38:32.370
I had you guard his tomb
in Jincheng for three years

38:32.370 --> 38:33.190
because I hoped you would use

38:33.190 --> 38:35.450
that time to think this through clearly.

38:36.070 --> 38:37.000
Did His Majesty

38:38.230 --> 38:40.160
and the late Crown Prince Maocheng

38:40.550 --> 38:42.360
not share blood ties?

38:43.480 --> 38:45.080
But what happened in the end?

38:53.670 --> 38:56.070
I, Li Yan, will heed
Your Majesty's teachings

38:56.070 --> 38:57.070
and keep

38:57.920 --> 38:59.360
your words in mind.

39:01.880 --> 39:02.960
Your Majesty, I...

39:02.960 --> 39:03.690
Attendants!

39:06.800 --> 39:08.400
Escort the Prince of Luo out.

39:35.030 --> 39:36.360
What my mother has lost,

39:37.150 --> 39:39.280
I will win back for her.

39:46.800 --> 39:47.660
Your Highness!

39:57.710 --> 39:58.710
Your Highness.

40:27.150 --> 40:28.880
Only one little Heir Apparent?

40:28.920 --> 40:29.550
Yes,

40:30.030 --> 40:31.320
only one.

40:31.840 --> 40:33.300
Wait outside for a moment.

40:33.630 --> 40:35.560
The weather has turned cold today.

40:36.030 --> 40:38.880
The little Heir Apparent needs
an additional layer of clothing

40:38.880 --> 40:40.080
lest he catch a chill.

40:40.280 --> 40:40.880
Yes.

41:03.030 --> 41:03.830
Your Majesty.

41:11.250 --> 41:12.050
Your Majesty,

41:12.240 --> 41:13.480
why did you hand the Prince of Chang's son

41:13.480 --> 41:14.550
to that matron?

41:43.480 --> 41:44.280
Zhuge Yue,

41:44.480 --> 41:45.670
you and I are different.

41:45.670 --> 41:47.870
There has always been a gulf between us.

41:48.350 --> 41:49.020
Chu...

41:50.630 --> 41:52.800
Since he chose to leave first,

41:53.110 --> 41:55.710
it means he's found something
more important.

41:57.150 --> 41:58.070
Chu,

41:58.760 --> 42:00.200
no matter where you run,

42:00.360 --> 42:01.960
I will find you.

42:02.150 --> 42:02.960
Zhuge Yue,

42:03.440 --> 42:05.800
when you wake up, forget about me.
